lead_paragraph: For the pundits who predicted 2016 would be the year New Zealand's stranglehold on world rugby starts to slip, results from the early rounds of Super Rugby must make for grim reading.

headline.print_headline: Analysis-Early Super Rugby Results Suggests No Demise in New Zealand
